{"tid":144600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去完摘士多啤梨，我覺得部分香港人真係垃撚圾","createTime":"2017-03-05T13:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T18:22:55.000Z","uid":7775,"like":223,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"933a9606666c7418e54e1c8a37f65e694873e274","tid":144600,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:57:32.000Z","msg":"今日小弟去本地士多啤梨園<br />\n(摘完過磅計錢)<br />\n<br />\n見到有個小朋友將摘咗一盒滿既士多啤梨倒瀉接近兩成<br />\n<br />\n之後佢老母話: 「跌咗就由佢啦，唔好要啦」<br />\n(其實又紅又飽滿，喺田度摘點都係要洗過先食)<br />\n<br />\n又有個小朋友喺度亂咁踩人地d農作物<br />\n佢老母都係輕聲咁話下佢:<br />\n「你唔可以咁踩嫁」<br />\n然後由得個小朋友繼續踩<br />\n<br />\n之後見到有樣野仲仆街<br />\n我見到有d士多啤梨好整齊咁放喺度<br />\n係好多行都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7fTxh6F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7fTxh6F.jpg&h=3ec6bb5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Rk4ryu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Rk4ryu.jpg&h=60a018ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n估計係有d人剪完人地d士多啤梨最後又唔撚想要<br />\n<br />\n然後就咁放返喺度<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌佢地老母垃圾影撚衰香港人，死全家</span>"},{"pid":"1393fe41d3753c2930ae5bc5ce9fdd4675d0f58c","tid":144600,"uid":54576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:00:05.000Z","msg":"正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c9618355dabf7609929d308e26dfa6ea33faa97","tid":144600,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:01:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我自己摘都有規有矩<br />\n<br />\n最後發現有少少爛都照買照食"},{"pid":"091a6ecf5fd9ede8668cbd20bb9c568ce4b4080f","tid":144600,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:02:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9fb44095f0cc9