tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:01:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢類野好似係大陸搞先，起碼好多年前我已經見珠三角有，其實佢計過條數，點都有錢賺<br />\n<br />\n平時成本係農戶&rarr;運輸&rarr;批發&rarr;運輸&rarr;零售&rarr;客戶<br />\n<br />\n佢家陣係直接農戶&rarr;客戶，中間慳左好多成本</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連呢度都咁多垃圾你就明點解啦<br />\n點都有錢賺 有錢大晒呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSor 有錢的確大晒</blockquote><br />\n有錢買唔買到f22<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1893b812c185288ed3fb2c8ac8f45c5db6b086","tid":144600,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:07:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢類野好似係大陸搞先，起碼好多年前我已經見珠三角有，其實佢計過條數，點都有錢賺<br />\n<br />\n平時成本係農戶&rarr;運輸&rarr;批發&rarr;運輸&rarr;零售&rarr;客戶<br />\n<br />\n佢家陣係直接農戶&rarr;客戶，中間慳左好多成本</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連呢度都咁多垃圾你就明點解啦<br />\n點都有錢賺 有錢大晒呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSor 有錢的確大晒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n希望你出份糧<br />\n日日俾老細當狗屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7c3881ff77baaa9130b89036f571077d7fde4c","tid":144600,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"